{"tid":99893,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[短故][創意產業] 我嘅職業係：代人去飲","createTime":"2017-01-29T14:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T13:39:54.000Z","uid":51000,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33fec4aa5cbf1c3e9f37a097df3af38b41eaf228","tid":99893,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:33:18.000Z","msg":"「去飲好悶？<br />\n明明同對新人唔熟，又要浪費一個寶貴嘅夜晚，睇你根本唔關心嘅成長片段......<br />\n只需三百蚊，還你自由身！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，之前我失業，捱咗幾晚面包，覺得生無可戀，<br />\n<br />\n就混咗入人地個婚宴度，大吃大喝。<br />\n<br />\n食到一半，聽到有兩個女人討論：「唉，成九點先開始上菜，十一點都唔知有無得走。」<br />\n<br />\n「係囉，本來今晚同男友睇演唱會，但係經理結婚，又唔敢唔黎。」<br />\n<br />\n「唉，如果可以悶少晚，畀多幾百蚊我都制。」<br />\n<br />\n呢段對話喺我腦海盤旋，散席果陣，<br />\n我決定要投身呢個拯救人類嘅行業：代人去飲。<br />\n<br />\n由痴飲痴食，升級到又食又拎，我覺得自己係天才。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我喺各大論壇開post，生意相當唔錯，<br />\n發展「創意產業」果然係岩嘅。<br />\n<br />\n香港每年有幾萬人結婚，就算得10%擺酒，每日都有十場酒席，<br />\n<br />\n而每場酒席，唔想去而又不得不去嘅，你估止唔止十個？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFB連載：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tomato0728chan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftomato0728chan&d=L9WWkC8qCnSwgTnBr0z%2BTGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=243e1410\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tomato0728chan</a>"},{"pid":"d6ea06db67a9a5055d12db70d05798110359e6f7","tid":99893,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:04:28.000Z","msg":"次次擺酒都請幾百人，新郎新娘邊有可能記得，<br />\n<br />\n都係靠門口張簽到紙，加埋數人情，先知邊個無到。<br />\n<br />\n我非常盡責，每次都會影相，即場Send比個客，<br />\n等佢upload FB、IG，講「新娘好索啊！祝你地白頭到老」。<br />\n<br />\n新人睇到FB，都唔會懷疑個客無去。<br />\n<br />\n至於點解無合照？<br />\n遲咗黎、咁岩去咗廁所......其實無人會問。<br />\n<br />\n人際關係係雙向嘅，你無興趣去飲，<br />\n係因為你同對新人唔熟，至少唔係「真心熟」，<br />\n<br />\n所以新人都唔會同你熟，唔會熟到喺芸芸賓客中，發現少咗你個人頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我亦遇過小麻煩，例如客人係去同事婚宴，<br />\n咁我坐落客人個位，同枱都係客人嘅同事，大家被困喺婚宴場地，<br />\n<br />\n難免有八卦女人問：「咦，你係邊個？XX（我個客）去咗邊？」<br />\n<br />\n待續..."},{"pid":"88922b7e640e7fa939e43b732d9c48ccf9ab09bc","tid":99893,"uid":31419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"幾得意 lm"},{"pid":"cd2ff99e7a337b2e93e719a4546cc5bfb2f9d99f","tid":99893,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾得意 lm</blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab9b6f4404664b901049662fe5ee28f1b329664","tid":99893,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a10a748d089b33d5709920e902782b0bebb394","tid":99893,"uid":20383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"題材幾特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46cb6814788fdef97d25f9740802b08d81c6d8f","tid":99893,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:19:51.000Z","msg":"interesting"},{"pid":"7206a56505715c73564e3d5651c33fab407e0cdf","tid":99893,"uid":369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:44:20.000Z","msg":"幾得意既題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ec11fcd4f9972e5fafa69e68e7e0390df2b128","tid":99893,"uid":78767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"題材新穎，文筆生鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc60702ab35f4a46191cc85fa9e768a1241aa9f2","tid":99893,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"又有新故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1869cb172777853c89f6c7622e49b69b9d8e0c39","tid":99893,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"樓豬快啲出文啦"},{"pid":"a5e8f37cbf6a5baa799ea5f10033174629e6d83e","tid":99893,"uid":51164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1e5083a9df8d9912e46dd5550b26f24521552c","tid":99893,"uid":12183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31081ae2fdbc0f23c20ce85df98f61899c034521","tid":99893,"uid":69206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01f9bebbd27052d2f06900fea2b2151de734f5a","tid":99893,"uid":77538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:01:33.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2479637b44fcc199f938639bc8be07aeee93dfc2","tid":99893,"uid":77631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有創意"},{"pid":"926227a5848941b9fa8ccf5a18959ec16bee8e6c","tid":99893,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"難免有八卦女人問：「咦，你係邊個？XX（我個客）去咗邊？」<br />\n<br />\n我會答：「XX晏啲先到，我係佢兄弟，<br />\n咁岩喺附近，幫佢霸住位影下相先。<br />\n咦，你件衫好靚！」<br />\n<br />\n無女人會深究我個垃圾解釋，佢地只係聽到「你件衫好靚」，<br />\n<br />\n我再讚埋佢地皮膚靚、身材好、髮質好......<br />\n無人會發現XX成晚都無到。<br />\n<br />\n實驗證明，人類最關心嘅，都係自己。<br />\n<br />\n因此，大家都知去飲好悶，但結婚依然會請飲。<br />\n<br />\n呃，人人都話，要搞個特別嘅婚宴，<br />\n<br />\n但根據我全職去飲嘅經驗，除咗有啲鮑魚特別細隻，其他野都無乜特別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過咗半年，生意開始難做。<br />\n<br />\n呢份工無須學歷、無須工作經驗，連體力都唔太需要，<br />\n簡直係廢青之選，梗係愈黎愈多競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n有競爭就有價格戰，壓到100蚊都有人做， <br />\n<br />\n我唔想同佢地一齊做爛市，<br />\n我決定增值自己，提供特別服務！"},{"pid":"d9e297209aeed852d1a731d21d9b37a62bdc3d30","tid":99893,"uid":51000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又有新故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日都係度寫故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61aedb38621546415655a9cc82f81414f68c2986","tid":99893,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"睇來樓主對結婚有好大怨氣"},{"pid":"a0135d539d086d878bfaa380a20197f32bd32415","tid":99893,"uid":35080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又有新故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日都係度寫故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n快啦屌你"},{"pid":"44d1b4af7a32509c73ee84903d851d070e4a1051","tid":99893,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"65ee0b6f28e96cc9ede1ee56c0234d750b5be0d2","tid":99893,"uid":77538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631e09a5da41945a18826e799d89c439ec843623","tid":99893,"uid":12964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6755b25be5fa520881d03a1c8537cb837256c483","tid":99893,"uid":61761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c92a987d9b22d199e5b8d8d2ebeea0a8877a556f","tid":99893,"uid":69206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"文文文文文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}